  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc7\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0ba8\u0baa\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0b9f\u0bb2\u0bae\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0bae\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A person who drowned in a reservoir was recovered as a dead body",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Thalawakala police said that yesterday (15) a dead body of a male was recovered from the Upper Kothmalai reservoir under Thalawakala police division.",
        "While the said person was struggling for his life as he was struggling for life in the reservoir, despite the efforts of local people, police, special operations forces and youths, his life could not be saved. He drowned in water.",
        "His dead body was recovered. It has been revealed that the person recovered as a dead body is Subpaiah Subramaniam aged 61 years old and father of two children from Vattagodai Madakumpura South.",
        "The police have conducted multi-angle investigations regarding whether the rescued man was dragged into the water or he fell into the water reservoir.",
        "The police further informed that the body has been sent to Nuwara Eliya District Hospital for post-mortem examination."
      ],
